item.description: Hello world ! The goal of the pages are to remember for myself what I did with my dedicated server. They will be planty of pages and crashed, always feel free to message me. Kimsufi KS-3C For all my experiment, I at the moment use a dedicated server having the following configuration : - i3-2130 - 8GB - 2To - Ubuntu Server 18.04 "Bionic Beaver" LTS (64bits) Current hosted services Docker Transmission
